Phillips Exeter Cube Day 2016 Heats!

Hello Competitor, below you will find your heats for your events.

Please bring your puzzles to the scrambling area once your heat has been called.

If you miss your heat, that’s okay, because we’ll have a last call. 

If you don’t see your scorecard, come back during last call.

If you miss last call, don’t worry, we’re nice and we have a second last call just to be safe!
